The,Amazon,Elastic,Transcoder,is,a,cloud,based,web,service,that,provides,developers,and,businesses,with,a,way,of,converting,or,transcoding,video,files,into,other,formats,The,Elastic,Transcoder,service,is,designed,to,be,easy,to,use,It,comes,with,presets,for,popular,output,formats,and,can,create,multiple,renditions,of,the,same,content,in,one,job,Users,are,given,precise,control,over,the,scaling,cropping,matting,and,stretching,of,their,videos,Elastic,Transcoder,users,can,transcode,up,to,minutes,of,video,for,free,each,month,After,that,users,pay,based,on,the,number,of,minutes,and,the,resolution,of,the,video,they,need,to,transcode,All,of,the,service,s,features,are,available,through,the,AWS,Management,Console,and,via,REST,API